Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.17,0:23:17.17,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}言葉にはない　形にもない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.17,0:23:20.92,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}ここにしか無い君がいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:25.93,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}はじまりの鐘の音が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:30.06,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}鳴り響く空　雲をかき分け　ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.06,0:23:33.60,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}世界を包んでいく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:38.86,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}踏み出す勇気抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.86,0:23:41.23,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}届いていて　今
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.23,0:23:46.11,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}瞳に　映るこの奇跡には
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:51.12,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}夢のはじまりの合図が鳴る
Comment: 0,0:22:31.62,0:22:35.08,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}I’ll always believe tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.63,0:22:46.01,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}映照在目光深处的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:49.39,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}给了我前行的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.39,0:22:54.69,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}将各种意义  托付在这只手中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:58.69,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}未曾注意到  几乎被忘记的情谊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:02.20,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}走过的景色  逐渐模糊消失
Comment: 0,0:23:02.20,0:23:04.16,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}Until you can’t see it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.16,0:23:08.41,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}不管沾染多少污渍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.41,0:23:14.17,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}全部被装进玩具箱的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.17,0:23:17.17,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}有着无法形容  没有实体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.17,0:23:20.92,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}只存在于这里的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:25.93,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}开始的钟声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:30.06,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}响彻天空  将云朵拨开  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.06,0:23:33.60,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}渐渐环绕着整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:38.86,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}怀着踏出第一步的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.86,0:23:41.23,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}现在将声音送出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.23,0:23:46.11,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}这映照在眼中的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:51.12,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)\blur5\bord0\c&H000000&}奏响了梦想开始的暗号
